How to add a new item check
===========================

Moving windmill guard in leaf check to a chest in mezame
 - deterministic - don't add the PersonData anymore, instead add chest
 - add zebuStudentGivesItem() method to flagset, activate .ifdef
 - instead add new spawn to mezame - fix npc pattern
 - consider renaming rom.flags.ZebuStudent

New item
 - allocate an itemget id (49..4f are free, use them now?)
   - notate in tables/item to keep track
   - add itemget flag (149) to Flags
   - no need to update rom.slots
